# App Router Boundaries

Default to Server Components in `app/`.

## Rules

- Do not add `'use client'` unless the file needs browser-only behavior.
- Use `'use client'` for hooks (`useState`, `useEffect`), DOM APIs, and interactive libraries like Headless UI.
- Keep client boundaries as small as possible by moving interactivity into leaf components.
- Prefer data fetching in Server Components when possible.
- Avoid passing non-serializable props from Server Components to Client Components.

## Quick check

- Can this render without JavaScript? Keep it server.
- Does this require user interaction state? Make only that component client.
